/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其他突如其來投資機會如是<br />\n<br />\n成日怨冇機會<br />\n咁機會黎到時你又有冇預先準備好自己令自己更有能力去捉緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好野呀你，哪裡來咁多機會</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n機會既野話黎就黎<br />\n唔會到時先俾時間你去準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n預先裝備好自己點都有著數<br />\n可以機會一黎就捉得住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申親身經歷加朋友經歷都係咁</blockquote><br />\n有儲錢<br />\n金融風暴個啲咪可以撈貨囉<br />\n有資產先可以搵到錢<br />\n<br />\n仲有及時行樂無問題<br />\n不過唔好生仔囉</blockquote><br />\n完全同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n要人生路行得順暢過人<br />\n點都要犧牲少少娛樂<br />\n<br />\n都係講緊少少姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大學個陣無攞曬啲錢去洗 攞曬去買股票<br />\n靜係攞股息都夠 一年去多幾次旅行<br />\n其實個人係輕鬆好多 唔洗咩都度住曬</blockquote><br />\n咁勁揪<br />\n巴打勁野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外俾多個隔離po樓主參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n女朋友條件比自己好真係好慘<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/352423/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/352423/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n到時想俾好生活女朋友都做唔到其實都慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6343547738e10e9125ab4d779a2a1a39a958d0e","tid":352310,"uid":119609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T01:25:51.000Z","msg":"儲錢唔一定買樓，例如你想買一個你好鐘意，唔買唔得既模型要240k你就要儲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84baa895dea9f8aadad83833d746c2b688bd232c","tid":352310,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T01:26:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>儲錢唔一定買樓，例如你想買一個你好鐘意，唔買唔得既模型要240k你就要儲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\